---
layout: page
title: "Meus trabalhos"
permalink: "/portfolio/index.html"
description: "Uma seleção de projetos variando de desenvolvimento front-end ao design de interface, focada em
performance e usabilidade."
---

{% set projects = portfolio.projects %}
{% set categories = portfolio.categories %}
{% set stats = portfolio.stats %}

<section class="mt-12 sm:mt-6 lg:mt-8 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-6 py-12 max-w-7xl">
  {% for project in projects %}
  <article class="group flex lg:flex-row flex-col items-center gap-12 lg:gap-24 portfolio-item">
    <figure
      class="border border-brand-dark-950 dark:border-border-dark rounded-xl w-full lg:w-1/2 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500">
      <img alt="{{ project.imageAlt or project.title }}"
        class="w-full object-cover aspect-video transition-transform duration-500" src="{{ project.image }}">
    </figure>
    <div class="space-y-6 w-full lg:w-1/2">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <span class="font-bold text-brand-red-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
          {{ project.category | join(' e ') or "Redesign & Acessibilidade" }}
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg text-brand-dark-500">
          <a href="{{ project.url or project.links.demo }}">{{ project.title }}</a>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        {{ project.description }}
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {% for tech in project.technologies %}
        <span class="bg-brand-dark-950 px-3 py-1 dark:bg-border-dark rounded-full text-sm">{{ tech }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</section>

<section class="mx-auto mb-32 px-6 container">
  <div class="space-y-8 p-12 md:p-20 border border-brand-gray-200/30 rounded-3xl text-center">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-brand-blue-500 text-4xl md:text-5xl">Vamos construir algo juntos?</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg">
      Estou sempre aberto a novos projetos, mentorias e colaborações interessantes em engenharia de software e design.
    </p>
    <div class="flex sm:flex-row flex-col justify-center items-center gap-6 pt-4">
      <a class="bg-brand-red-500 hover:bg-brand-red-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl w-full sm:w-auto font-bold text-lg no-underline transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 transform"
        href="/contato">
        Entre em contato
      </a>
      <a class="group flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold ttext-lg hover:underline" href="/cv">
        Veja meu currículo
        {% lucide "arrow-right", { class: "group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" } %}
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>